  "keyFeatures": [
    "Custom DSL for API contract definition with strong typing",
    "Multi-platform code generation (TypeScript, C#, F#, Dart, Kotlin, Swift)",
    "Built-in validation and type safety on both client and server",
    "Interactive playground for API exploration",
    "Automatic REST endpoints and Swagger generation",
    "Support for Node.js, .NET, Web, Android, iOS, and Flutter"
  ],
